content.rendered:
The Tromso range of contract desking is ideal for those who prefer a minimalist, practical and Scandinavian style. 

We also offer the Tromso Boardroom Table in an Oval.

The Tromso Boardroom Table comes with a 25mm thick rectangle table top made from contract grade laminate and a 2mm protective edge. Heat resistant and metal to metal fixings for total integrity. 

5 year guarantee. This item requires self assembly.
